    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained used car that has been cared for and continues to perform reliably. The exterior presents nicely overall, with only minor signs of normal wear such as light surface scratches consistent with everyday use; no significant dents or structural damage. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery and trim showing modest wear appropriate for its age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, with no major issues to report \u2014 routine maintenance has been kept up, and the engine and transmission operate smoothly. This is a solid, dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for reliable transportation without paying new-car prices.",
