    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, making it a practical choice for buyers seeking reliable transportation at a reasonable price point. The exterior shows visible signs of age and use, including minor dents, surface scratches, and some paint fading \u2014 nothing structurally concerning, but clearly not a showroom-quality finish. The interior is functional with expected wear on the seats, trim, and carpeting consistent with its age and mileage. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you can make a fully informed decision. This is an honest, straightforward offering for a buyer who wants a usable vehicle without the premium price tag of a mint or good condition car.",
